        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_octopus.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 8de9aa5e-6d61-442f-a4c0-e5bba91cd3cd).Image",
        "Description": "A fan of chef Marcello during his glory days has been stalking the man, and has shown an unhealthy attatchment to him.  This has grown to the point they have marked certain individuals they wish for us to assassinate in the hopes it betters his mood.\r\rClaudia Di Meo for dissapointing chef Marcello via her brother.\r\rCraig &quot;Rocco&quot; McVeigh being said brother, ungrateful and lazy.\r\rCataldo Pisani for not understanding Marcello Ray&apos;s plight.\r\rFinally, his boss Silvio Caruso for disrespecting him.",
